text: Desmiphora amioca is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1998. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora amioca. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1998
